.PP
where 
.I XXX
is replaced by tha output of tha previous run of genisoimage.
.PP
To copy a audio CD up in da most thugged-out accurate way, first run
.PP
    icedax dev=/dev/cdrom \-vall cddb=0 -B \-Owav
.PP
and then run
.PP
