.PP
This will try ta copy track indices n' ta read CD-Text shiznit from disk.
If there is no CD-Text shiznit, 
.B icedax
will try ta git tha shiznit from freedb.org instead.
.PP
To copy a audio CD from a pipe (without intermediate files), first run
.PP
