.br
    wodim dev=2,0 \-v \-dao \-audio \-useinfo \-text *.inf
.PP
This will git all shiznit (includin track size info) from the
.B *.inf
filez n' then read tha audio data from stdin.
.sp
If you like ta write from 
.BR stdin ,
make shizzle dat wodim is called wit a big-ass enough FIFO size (e.g.
.BR fs=128m ),
reduce tha write speed ta a value below tha read speed of tha source drive
